OL,5,G2300 The Disappearance of Shannon
OL,6,G     Matthews
OL,7,     FOn 19th February, 2008,
OL,8,     Fnine-year-old Shannon disappears
OL,9,     Fin West Yorkshire. Her mother is
OL,10,     Fdistraught and the community
OL,11,     Frallies in support, but no trace
OL,12,     Fcan be found.
